rows.label: qst202411_msg0001
rows.name:
Waahh I ate way too much.
My tummy is gonna explode.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't think I'm gonna be able to
look at a bowl of fried mice again
any time soon.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0003
rows.name:
Ibuki mean rice.
Mice were not consumed.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0004
rows.name:
Haha, Ibuki.
Never change.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0005
rows.name: But you did good. Well done!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0006
rows.name:
Well that's because I'm just
an all-round amazing Blade.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0007
rows.name: You did good too, R...uh, Rex.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0008
rows.name:
...Is there something about my
name that's hard to say, or what?

rows.label: qst202411_msg0009
rows.name:
Haha, good old Ibuki!
The forgetfulness is growing on me.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0010
rows.name:
It was a job well done, anyway.
Kudos!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0011
rows.name: Thanks, Nina! You too!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0012
rows.name:
I, that's not, uh-
Whatever, I can't be bothered...

rows.label: qst202411_msg0013
rows.name:
Hm...
Ibuki's memory hasn't improved.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0014
rows.name: Still, you did well. Bravo.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0015
rows.name: Thanks, Morodge!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0016
rows.name:
You're most welcome.
I also feel like I should remind you
of my name. It's Meleph.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0017
rows.name: Ah Ibuki, you lovable birdbrain you.

rows.label: qst202411_msg0018
rows.name:
But you did good today,
and that's a fact. Congrats!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0019
rows.name: Thanks, Zeke! Congrats to both of us!

rows.label: qst202411_msg0020
rows.name:
So I realized this some time ago,
but how come you never get my
name wrong?

rows.label: qst202411_msg0021
rows.name:
I should probably be flattered, but
it almost feels like not being invited
to a party...
